data.title: John Boozman for U.S. Senate
data.meta_description: John Boozman, a successful businessman and life-long resident of Arkansas, has represented Arkansas in the United States Senate for six years, establishing a record as a strong supporter of the values and principles that Arkansans hold dearly.
data.text:
I go to work every day in Washington to stand up for Arkansas values and our families. I am taking action to curb inflation, secure our borders, defend our constitutional rights, and push back radical leftist agendas. I worked with President Trump to put America First and put three judges on the Supreme Court. I will never stop working for Arkansas.

Thank you for your interest in volunteering. You can participate in big or small ways to help re-elect Senator John Boozman. Every effort makes a difference.

Do you want to hear what John Boozman is doing as he goes to work for you everyday?

John Boozman, a successful businessman and life-long resident of Arkansas, has established a record as a strong supporter of the values and principles that Arkansans hold dearly. He will continue this same commitment to the people of the Natural State as your United States Senator. Stay Connected!
